---
// Contact.astro - Sección de contacto con diseño estilo Ferxxo
---

<section id="contact" class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden bg-ferxxo-black">
  <!-- Elementos decorativos de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <!-- Gradiente en esquina -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-bl from-ferxxo-pink/20 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-tr from-ferxxo-blue/20 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Elementos gráficos -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/4 left-10 w-20 h-20 border border-ferxxo-purple/20 rounded-full"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-10 w-40 h-40 border border-ferxxo-green/20 rounded-full"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Líneas de distorsión -->
    <div
      class="glitch-line absolute top-1/4 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-ferxxo-pink/30"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="glitch-line delay-700 absolute top-2/3 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-ferxxo-blue/30"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <!-- Encabezado de sección -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white"
        data-aos="fade-up"
      >
        <span class="neon-text-purple">CONTACTO</span>
      </h2>
      <div
        class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-ferxxo-pink to-ferxxo-purple mx-auto"
        data-aos="zoom-in"
        data-aos-delay="200"
      >
      </div>
      <p
        class="mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto text-gray-400"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="300"
      >
        ¿Quieres colaborar o tienes alguna pregunta? Envíame un mensaje y me
        pondré en contacto contigo lo antes posible.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-stretch max-w-6xl mx-auto"
    >
      <!-- Formulario de contacto -->
      <div
        class="relative p-1 overflow-hidden group rounded-2xl"
        data-aos="fade-right"
        data-aos-delay="400"
      >
        <!-- Borde con efecto neón -->
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-ferxxo-pink via-ferxxo-purple to-ferxxo-blue opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 blur-md transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>

        <!-- Formulario -->
        <div
          class="relative bg-ferxxo-black/90 p-8 rounded-2xl h-full backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-white tracking-wide">
            ENVÍAME UN <span class="text-ferxxo-pink">MENSAJE</span>
          </h3>

          <form class="space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <!-- Nombre -->
              <div class="relative">
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="name"
                  placeholder="Nombre"
                  class="w-full bg-ferxxo-black/50 border border-ferxxo-pink/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-ferxxo-pink focus:shadow-glow-sm transition-shadow duration-300"
                  required
                />
              </div>

              <!-- Email -->
              <div class="relative">
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  placeholder="Email"
                  class="w-full bg-ferxxo-black/50 border border-ferxxo-blue/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-ferxxo-blue focus:shadow-glow-sm transition-shadow duration-300"
                  required
                />
              </div>

              <!-- Asunto -->
              <div class="relative">
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="subject"
                  placeholder="Asunto"
                  class="w-full bg-ferxxo-black/50 border border-ferxxo-purple/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-ferxxo-purple focus:shadow-glow-sm transition-shadow duration-300"
                />
              </div>

              <!-- Mensaje -->
              <div class="relative">
                <textarea
                  id="message"
                  rows="5"
                  placeholder="Tu mensaje"
                  class="w-full bg-ferxxo-black/50 border border-ferxxo-green/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-ferxxo-green focus:shadow-glow-sm transition-shadow duration-300 resize-none"
                  required></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Botón de enviar -->
            <div class="relative group">
              <div
                class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-ferxxo-pink to-ferxxo-purple rounded-lg blur opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-200"
              >
              </div>
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="relative w-full py-3 bg-ferxxo-black border border-transparent rounded-lg font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider group-hover:text-ferxxo-pink transition duration-200"
              >
                Enviar Mensaje
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Información de contacto y mapa -->
      <div class="flex flex-col" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="500">
        <!-- Tarjeta de información -->
